>>>>>>> We are the UK’s leading charitable funder of diabetes research. We
improve lives through pioneering research into all forms of diabetes and
diabetes-related complications. The work we support helps us understand the
causes of diabetes, bring about life-changing breakthroughs in care, treatment
and prevention and bring us closer to a cure. In 2019 we invested over £6.8
million in diabetes research and agreed to support 35 new studies.
